      "blocks": {
        "88eb7521-5fbd-4422-8909-b536b89798c4": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>What is EVA material?</p>",
            "des": "<p>EVA stands for ethylene vinyl acetate, a lightweight and flexible material with waterproof properties. Because the material is hypoallergenic, the mats do not emit any odors, even at high temperatures.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "dbc7822b-1065-4071-ba4a-4dd0547c956a": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>What are the advantages of using EVA material in car mats?</p>",
            "des": "<p>EVA material has many advantages, such as resistance to wear, durability, lightness, flexibility, and shape retention.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "1e9afcfe-c8c1-452a-87d9-a16d1fd3b19f": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>What sizes of mats are available for cars?</p>",
            "des": "<p>The dimensions of car mats may vary depending on the car model.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "575491bc-94bb-4c01-a70c-5fbf1197f048": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>What if I need a custom mat?</p>",
            "des": "<p>It is possible to make a separate mat for a gas bottle if it protrudes in the trunk or to cover a larger floor area in specific places as requested by the customer.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "c7bf539b-36fa-4be1-9663-46bfaf0c4cba": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>Can the trunk be made in 2 parts?</p>",
            "des": "<p>Since the product is custom-made, for a 7-seater car, we can also divide the trunk into 2 parts, so the user can easily fold the third row without needing to remove the mat from the trunk.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "3b89d29a-8c60-4a6b-b981-1aba2b1f42c9": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>What colors are available for the mats?</p>",
            "des": "<p>Over 150 colors to choose from. Various colors of mats and edging are available, allowing you to stand out among other car owners.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "5aa5b147-4f1f-41b9-aa57-88465558f7f5": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>How to properly install mats made of EVA material?</p>",
            "des": "<p>Each set has a specific type of fastening; we have over 30 types. Fastenings are attached in the appropriate places, and we also sew Velcro on the sides to prevent mats from shifting and ensure they stay in place.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "9bcc9929-31c3-4b08-ad69-9a145c857f09": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>Can EVA mats be washed?</p>",
            "des": "<p>Yes, mats can be washed with a soft sponge and detergent. However, aggressive chemical cleaners are not recommended.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "eb4517e5-ab48-4945-a66b-d963d5c2fc58": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>Can EVA mats be used in winter?</p>",
            "des": "<p>Yes, the mats can be used in winter as they have properties that protect against cold and moisture.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        },
        "c3b94ada-1361-4b31-84ef-332a22e6dea6": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "category": "",
            "hd": "<p>Do the mats have a warranty?</p>",
            "des": "<p>We provide a one-year warranty from the date of receiving the mats, allowing the set to be replaced with a new one within a year in case of deformation or any detected wear. Thanks to the good quality of the material, the mats last 5-7 years.</p>",
            "des_html": ""
          }
        }
      },
